title: Special PancakeSquad NFT holders IFO  allocation
body:
As New NFT market is created on PCS and those who believe and are strong holders of Cake have invested on NFTs of PCS. In order to increase the demand for NFTs and reward the holders what about adding some important utility for PancakeSquad NFT holders?
This will increase the market volume and demand for NFTs also accelerate the CAKE burns which impact the CAKE price 🚀 as a result of more cake buyback and 🔥🔥

So the proposal is:

Can we have special allocation for PancakeSquad NFT holders? 

Example: Allocate x% amount of X IFO tokens available distributed equally to NFT holders with a max limit for each Pancakesquad NFT profile in order to be fairly distributed as a reward for holding these NFTS .

This will increase Pancakesquad NFT demands and volume traded on NFT market also users with small cake amount will be rewarded for holding cake.
What do you think so for special IFO allocation for PancakeSquad NFT holders?
choices: YES-Create IFO allocation for PS NFT HOLDERS
author: 0x5fee6967D10a15Bbe63A616E125362b9E3392360
